# Dependency and build outputs are recreated inside the image.
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
coverage
**/coverage

# Local evidence, diagnostics, caches, and mutable operator state.
*.log
**/*.log
.agent_checkpoint
**/.agent_checkpoint
release-evidence-manifest.json
migration-verification.log
manager-typecheck.log
production-boundary-tests.log
manager-image-build.log
signed-resource-revocation.log

# Local secrets and environment overlays never enter the build context.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Editor and OS noise.
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
.vscode
**/.vscode
.idea
**/.idea

# Repository-only material not required to compile or run the production image.
memory
**/memory
wiki
**/wiki
docs
**/docs
